
'''Nyigbla Afahyɛ''' afahyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Afife a ɛbɛn Akatsi wɔ Frao Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so mienu no mu<ref>https://ghanamps.com/constituency/details.php?id=2475</ref><ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>.

== Afahyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi afahyɛ de da ase na afei nso, wɔde kae bere a Anlo-ewe fo no tu firii wɔn kane tenabea baa faako a wɔn te sesei no<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>.

